    • updateViewModel

      public void updateViewModel()
      updateViewModel() This method is called at the end of every ReadThread method which implements the Server-Client communication protocol messages, by calling the updateViewModels method of the DataModelManager These methods of ReadThread manipulate the Data of the DataModelManager. Therefore after the manipulation the GameStartViewModel has to fetch the updates. This is realized with the updateViewModel method.
